links.title: Amazon, Apple, Google & Facebook Earnings Summary
links.description: Amazon ( AMZN) crushed Wall Street expectations, beating on earnings (+192% y/y growth) and revenues (+37% y/y growth). Operating margins improved from 4.51% to 6.44%, and profit margins improved from 3.05% to 6.58%. AWS revenue grew 29% (Azure grew 48%), and the company forecasted Q4 revenue growth between 28% and 29% - above estimates.
